<div id="chat-column" class="column col-chat">
  <!-- ===================== Chat Header ===================== -->
  <section>
    <div class="panel__body panel__body--chat-meta">
      <div class="ui-inline-gap-2-mb2">
        <span class="badge status-badge status-chat">
          <i class="fa-solid fa-comments chat-icon-inline"></i>채팅
        </span>
        <span class="chat-channel-label">
          웹채팅 &gt; 일반상담
        </span>
      </div>
      <div class="chat-customer-meta">
        <span class="badge status-badge status-unauth">
          <i class="fa-solid fa-lock chat-icon-inline"></i>무인증
        </span>
        <span class="ui-title-base">박민지(여)</span>
        <span class="chat-text-subtle">|</span>
        <span class="chat-investment-label">투자성향(적극형)</span>
      </div>
    </div>
    <header class="panel-header main-live-header">
      <span class="weight-semibold">실시간 채팅 상담</span>
      <div class="main-live-header-actions">
        <div class="main-live-search-wrap">
          <input
            type="text"
            placeholder="검색어를 입력하세요"
            class="field placeholder-blue-200 chat-search-input"
          />
          <i class="fa-solid fa-magnifying-glass main-live-search-icon"></i>
        </div>
        <button class="main-live-pause-btn">
          <i class="fa-solid fa-pause"></i>
        </button>
      </div>
    </header>
  </section>

  <!-- ===================== Messages ===================== -->
  <section class="chat__messages">
    <div class="chat-date-row">
      <span class="badge badge--date">2024년 2월 12일 월요일</span>
    </div>
    <div class="main-live-msg main-live-msg--customer">
      <div class="main-live-msg-meta">
        <i class="fa-regular fa-user main-live-user-icon"></i>
        <span class="main-live-customer-text">박민지</span>
      </div>
      <div class="chat-bubble customer main-live-bubble-elevated">
        안녕하세요. ISA 계좌 개설하고 싶은데 도움 받을 수 있을까요?
      </div>
      <span class="main-live-time-text main-live-msg-time">10:15</span>
    </div>
    <div class="main-live-msg main-live-msg--agent">
      <div class="main-live-msg-meta">
        <span class="main-live-time-text">10:16</span>
        <span class="main-live-agent-text">상담사 최서연</span>
      </div>
      <div class="chat-bubble agent main-live-bubble-elevated">
        안녕하세요, 박민지 고객님. 신한투자증권 상담사 최서연입니다. ISA 계좌 개설 도와드리겠습니다.
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="main-live-msg main-live-msg--customer">
      <div class="main-live-msg-meta">
        <i class="fa-regular fa-user main-live-user-icon"></i>
        <span class="main-live-customer-text">박민지</span>
      </div>
      <div class="chat-bubble customer main-live-bubble-elevated">
        ISA 계좌의 장점이 궁금합니다.
      </div>
      <div class="main-live-tag-row">
        <span class="tag-pill tag-pill--brand">ISA</span>
        <span class="tag-pill tag-pill--teal">혜택문의</span>
      </div>
      <span class="main-live-time-text main-live-msg-time">10:17</span>
    </div>
    <div class="main-live-msg main-live-msg--agent">
      <div class="main-live-msg-meta">
        <span class="main-live-time-text">10:18</span>
        <span class="main-live-agent-text">상담사 최서연</span>
      </div>
      <div class="chat-bubble agent main-live-bubble-elevated">
        ISA 계좌는 비과세 혜택이 큰 장점입니다. 일반형은 200만원, 서민형은 400만원까지 비과세가 적용되며, 초과분도
        9.9%의 분리과세로 절세 효과가 뛰어납니다.
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="main-live-msg main-live-msg--customer">
      <div class="main-live-msg-meta">
        <i class="fa-regular fa-user main-live-user-icon"></i>
        <span class="main-live-customer-text">박민지</span>
      </div>
      <div class="chat-bubble customer main-live-bubble-elevated">
        가입 조건은 어떻게 되나요?
      </div>
      <span class="main-live-time-text main-live-msg-time">10:19</span>
    </div>
    <div class="main-live-msg main-live-msg--agent">
      <div class="main-live-msg-meta">
        <span class="main-live-time-text">10:20</span>
        <span class="main-live-agent-text">상담사 최서연</span>
      </div>
      <div class="chat-bubble agent main-live-bubble-elevated">
        만 19세 이상 국내 거주자라면 누구나 가입 가능합니다. 근로소득이 있으신 분은 일반형, 총급여 5천만원 이하 또는
        종합소득 3800만원 이하는 서민형으로 가입하실 수 있습니다.
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="main-live-msg main-live-msg--customer">
      <div class="main-live-msg-meta">
        <i class="fa-regular fa-user main-live-user-icon"></i>
        <span class="main-live-customer-text">박민지</span>
      </div>
      <div class="chat-bubble customer main-live-bubble-elevated">
        바로 개설하고 싶은데 어떻게 하면 되나요?
      </div>
      <span class="main-live-time-text main-live-msg-time">10:21</span>
    </div>
    <div class="main-live-read-wrap">
      <div class="chat-read-marker">여기까지 읽었습니다.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="main-live-scroll-wrap">
      <button class="chat-scroll-bottom-btn">
        <i class="fa-solid fa-chevron-down"></i>
      </button>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ===================== Composer ===================== -->
  <section class="chat__composer">
    <div class="chat__actions">
      <button
        title="파일 첨부"
        class="chat__action-btn"
      >
        <i class="fa-solid fa-paperclip chat-action-icon-muted"></i>
      </button>
      <button
        title="이모티콘"
        class="chat__action-btn"
      >
        <i class="fa-regular fa-face-smile chat-action-icon-muted"></i>
      </button>
      <textarea
        placeholder="메시지를 입력하세요..."
        class="chat__input" data-role="chat-message-input"
        rows="3"
      ></textarea>
      <button class="chat__send-btn send-btn">
        <i class="fa-solid fa-paper-plane"></i>
        전송
      </button>
    </div>
  </section>
</div>
